# iRO API

iRO API is a simple API allowing clients to view the data of their iRO Databases.

# Group Public Data

## Public Project Collection [/data/{serial}/jobs/{sort}/{type}?{forceRefresh}]

### List all public projects [GET]

+ Parameters
    + serial: `12345-12345-12345` (text) - Serial of the target database
    + sort (enum[string], optional) - Sorting direction
        + Default: `desc`
        + Members
            + `asc`
            + `desc`
    + type (optional, enum[string])
        + Default: `normal`
        + Members
            + `normal`
            + `archiv`
    + forceRefresh (optional, boolean)
        + Default: false


