## Single public project [/data/{serial}/job-detail/{id}]

### Get detailed data of single public project [GET]

+ Parameters
    + serial: `12345-12345-12345` (text) - Serial of the target database
    + id: `1000` (number) - Project id

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Project Response)

# Data Structures

## Project (object)
+ fm_id: 1 (number) - Represents the project id in iRO
+ visible: 1 (number)
+ timestamp: 1486567471 (number)
+ importCalendarDay: 2017163 (number)
+ last_modified_date: `08.02.2017 16:24:31` (string)
+ last_modified: 1486567471 (number)
+ start_date: `2017-02-08` (string) - Field "Start"
+ formatter: 1 (enum[number]) - 1 for Standard format or 2 for Markdown format
    + 1 - Standard
    + 2 - Markdown
+ rewrite_link: `372-Salesmanager`
+ Web_Detailslink: `http://www.your-website.com/job/372` (string) - Link to your website, please contact us how you can specify this
+ seo_title: `Salesmanager, `
+ seo_desc (string)
+ position: `Salesmanager` (string) - Field "Projekt"
+ industry: `Halbleiter` (string) - Field "Branche"
+ location: `Berlin` (string) - Field "Ort"
+ job_intro (string) - Field "Anonyme Einleitung für Webseite" bzw "Web-Intro"
+ job_description - Field "Die Position"
+ job_candidate - Field "Der ideale Kandidat"
+ job_desirability - Field "Attraktivität der Aufgabe"
+ job_resume - Field "Schlusstext"
+ contact: `Max Müller` (string) - Field "Web Berater"
+ contact_mail: `max.mueller@gmail.com` (string) - Field "Web E-Mail"
+ lang: `de` (enum[string]) - Field "Sprache"
    + "de" - Deutsch
    + "en" - Englisch
+ full_text (string) - Computed value for text search functionality, contains all text fields

## Project Response
+ results (Project, required)